precis:
Regulations Amending the MOTOR VEHICLE SAFETY REGULATIONS (ROOF INTRUSION
PROTECTION) by revising Test Method 216 in order to make it more suitable
for testing the structural strength of vehicles with severely sloped,
raised or irregular roofs, and by harmonizing it with the method used by
the U.S. National Highway Traffic Safety Administration.
